pl.touk.hades.load
Class Load

java.lang.Object
  pl.touk.hades.load.Load
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Load
extends Object
implements Serializable

A holder for the main data source load level and the failover data source load level. If the two load levels are equal (for example both are low than this class can also hold information whether the main database load level is higher.

Instances of this class are immutable.

Author:
Michal Sokolowski
